<div class="modal-body printable" id="directDebitGuarantee-content">
<p>
		The data controllers responsible for processing this personal information are Aviva Health UK Limited as the administrator of the product, Aviva Insurance Limited as the insurer of the product and Aviva UK Digital Limited who are responsible for the sale and distribution of the product.
	</p>
<p>
		To get a quote from us, we (and our third parties) need to collect and use personal and health information relating to you and anyone else to be covered by this insurance. We will collect this information from what you tell us, from data we already hold (including from other quotes and policies with us), from publicly available sources and other organisations we trust and from data from your device, general location and how you interact with our website. 
	</p>
<p>
		We will use this information to verify your identity and help prevent fraud, calculate our risk to insure you, calculate your price, set up, assess and maintain your insurance contract with us, renew and make changes to your cover, process claims and carry out marketing and analytics. 
			</p>
<p>We will share this information within the Aviva Group, our insurers, reinsurers, brokers and other specific organisations for these purposes. 
			</p>
<p>We will also use automated software to make decisions relating to the above activities, including deciding what to charge for your cover. To ask us about how we make automatic decisions, call us on 0800 056 3008*.

			</p>
<p>You have various rights in relation to your personal data including accessing your data, and in some limited circumstances objecting to processing or having your data erased.

	</p>
<p>
To find out more details about your rights and how we use your personal data, please read the Privacy Policy or write to our Data Protection Officer by either emailing <a dataprt="" href="mailto:">DATAPRT@aviva.com</a> or writing to: AVIVA, Level 5, Pitheavlis, Perth, PH2Â 0NH
 
	</p><p>NOTE: If you have any concerns about our use of your data, you should not proceed with this application as we may be unable to provide you with a policy. You can also contact us at any time if you would like us to stop using your information but this may prevent us assessing future claims and the policy may be cancelled. </p>
